sequenceDiagram
  %% 完成形の1回の memory query シーケンス図: Mermaid UML sequenceDiagramで引用付き回答または棄権までを見る

  actor User as 人 / AI agent
  participant RX as research_x API
  participant Lens as SearchLens / RetrievalPolicy
  participant Route as ObjectiveRoutePolicy / Route Portfolio
  participant Guard as ProviderApiBudgetGuard
  participant Evidence as Source Bundle / Context / Citation
  participant Authority as AnswerAuthorityGatekeeper
  participant Boundary as Answer Boundary
  participant Trace as Workflow Trace / Eval

  User->>RX: query / objective / context budget / reviewed source candidate
  RX->>Trace: sidecar trace を開始
  RX->>Lens: corpus scope・source weights・inference stance
  Lens->>Route: 目的に合う候補経路を選ぶ

  par local candidate routes
    Route-->>Route: exact / SQLite FTS / BM25 / metadata / relation
  and expansion routes
    Route-->>Route: semantic vectors / Corpus2Skill / graph-topic hints
  and provider-backed routes
    Route->>Guard: OCR / Reader / rerank / external search / managed RAG
    Guard-->>Route: candidate or provider_gated skip
  end

  Route->>Evidence: candidates + restore_path + skip reason
  Evidence->>Evidence: source bundle -> context chunk -> citation
  Evidence->>Authority: specific claim supportを確認
  Authority->>Boundary: answer_support または停止理由
  Boundary->>Trace: answerability・citation coverage・route gapsを保存

  alt citation-ready supportあり
    Boundary-->>RX: answer with citations
    RX-->>User: 引用付き回答
  else support不足
    Boundary-->>RX: abstain / needs_review / source_not_restored / citation_missing / hypothesis_only / provider_gated
    RX-->>User: 理由つきで返す
  end
